==English==
===Noun===
'''circumcision''' ([[circumcisions]])

# The act of excising or amputating the [[foreskin]] or [[prepuce]] from the [[penis]].
# The act of excising tissue from the [[vulva]] of the female.

====Related terms====
*[[circumcise]], [[circumcize]]
*[[female circumcision]]

